HEADWORD: Pergolo
<hw>Per"go*lo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It.]</ety>
<def>A continuous colonnade or arcade; -- applied to the decorative
groups of windows, as in Venetian palazzi.</def>⟦br⟧
